tags.description: Urban Air Adventure Park Soccer Complex is a perfectly level 10-acre grass field complex that accommodates two small sided game fields and one full sided field.  Established in May 2000, the property has enough parking for over 90 vehicles.
tags.name: Urban Air Adventure Park Soccer Complex
